z

| Step | Hyp | Ref | Expression |

| 1 |  | euf.1 | |- ( ph -> A. y ph ) |

| 8 | 7 | #P_bibi2d | |- ( z = y -> ( ( ph <-> x = z ) <-> ( ph <-> x = y ) ) ) |
| 9 | 8 | #P_albidv | |- ( z = y -> ( A. x ( ph <-> x = z ) <-> A. x ( ph <-> x = y ) ) ) |

 A version of the existential uniqueness definition with a hypothesis instead of a distinct variable condition.  (Contributed by NM, 12-Aug-1993.)
